<Layout
	title="Who am I?"
	description="The question I keep asking myself."
	pubDate={new Date('June 09 2026')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		The question which gets asked in almost all situations of life, "who are you?".  Whether meeting new 
people, interviewing for jobs, networking, relationships with friends and family. What should be a relatively 
simple question to answer, I find more and more difficult to answer the further I go on in my journey. The 
sense of self is ever evolving. A son, a student, a worker, a friend, a lover. We play different roles for 
different people, and those roles are continuously changing as time ticks by. I am definitely not the first 
person to feel this question in this way, but at present I feel the question intensely. I suppose partially 
self inflicted with this venture into online lands. But it is a question I have been asking myself a lot recently. 
Trying to understand my place in the world. What am i doing? Where am I going? Ultimately, who am I?
 
	</p>

